(62, 'Aasmund Gabestad Nørsett', 'Northern Lego', '', '', 'My name is Aasmund and I\'m a 16 year old, Norwegian LEGO builder. I\'ve collected LEGO since I was three years old, but only started building MOCs about 2 years ago. I enjoy building Star Wars, Lord of the Rings and Medieval MOCs, but occasionally I build other themes such as City and Pirates of the Caribbean.', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWAAJQbQuZiWoK-7JJ6_IrA', 'https://www.flickr.com/photos/145356369@N04/', 'https://www.instagram.com/northern_lego/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'false', 'false'),
